		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />One more tiny feature request:
<br />
<br />-Have the nametable grid show attribute borders.   The grid is crowded already, but you could make just the corners of attribute blocks look a little different.  Or have a separate attribute grid that could be turned off and on like the other grids.  Today I was trying to find an optimal place to draw a text box to the screen and I had to strain my eyes a bit and touch the screen with my fingers to find a place where the corners of the textbox would line up right with the attributes.

		

		</td>
